			"a_h2": "Built From This",
			"a_description": "The distinctive visual aesthetic of Constructivism — a design approach that creates unique, memorable interfaces. Background: light (#f0ece8). The .inner panel has a clean background with subtle border treatment and appropriate border-radius. Colors: #cc2200 as the primary accent for interactive elements and highlights. #111111 for headings, #444444 for body text. The aesthetic captures the essence of constructivism through careful color choices, spacing, and visual weight. Set in Oswald — chosen for its visual character that complements this design style. Heading at weight 600-700, 24-28px, line-height 1.2-1.3. Eyebrow at weight 500, 11px, uppercase, 2-3px letter-spacing, color #cc2200. Body at weight 400, 14-15px, line-height 1.6-1.7, color #444444. Buttons: primary — #cc2200 background with contrasting text. Secondary: transparent with #cc2200 border. Alternatives: system-ui (universal fallback), sans-serif stack.",
